videos.description: Taylor Cornelius finds Tylan Wallace with a quick pass for an 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State opens scoring with quick slant for TD

videos.description: Taylor Cornelius airs it out to Landon Wolf, who catches the 42-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State goes deep for 42-yard TD pass

videos.description: Kwamie Lassiter II gets open and QB Carter Stanley finds him for the 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Lassiter uses double move to burn defender on Kansas TD

videos.description: Taylor Cornelius goes to the air again, finding Tyron Johnson for a 64-yard Oklahoma State touchdown.
videos.headline: Cornelius unloads for 3rd TD pass

videos.description: Kansas running back Pooka Williams Jr. breaks a few tackles and races up the middle for a 60-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Pooka Williams Jr. runs in Kansas TD from 60 yards out

videos.description: Justice Hill bounces to the outside and scores a 10-yard touchdown to extend Oklahoma State's lead over Kansas.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Hill scores 10-yard TD

videos.description: Kansas quarterback Carter Stanley finds Steven Sims Jr. wide open for a 31 -yard touchdown to cut into Oklahoma State's lead.
videos.headline: Kansas' Stanley completes 31-yard TD pass to Sims Jr.

videos.description: Carter Stanley throws his third touchdown pass of the game, this time to Jeremiah Booker from 22 yards out.
videos.headline: Kansas QB Stanley's 3rd TD pass goes to Booker
